('Tripplanner', 'tripplanner', 'Optimizes travel with AI-driven, personalized itinerary planning.', 'Imagine a tool that not only helps plan your trips but also optimizes them for the best possible experience. That''s what Tripplanner offers. As a frequent traveler and tech enthusiast, I''ve had my fair share of experiences with travel planning tools, but Tripplanner stands out with its AI-driven capabilities. Designed for everyone from vacationers to digital nomads, this tool simplifies the creation of itineraries by considering your preferences for sights, dining, and lodging to craft a personalized travel plan.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/3a69d1971d65319cbcc284df5f3e4c93cc5d0859-2484x1218.png', 'https://tripplanner.ai/', 'free', '[{"plan": "Free Access", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI-Powered Itinerary Creation","Optimal Route Planning","Local Cuisine Recommendations","Community-Driven Insights","User-Friendly Interface","Customization Options"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
