('FusionAds.ai', 'fusionads-ai', 'Revolutionize ad creation and testing with AI-powered efficiency.', 'In the bustling world of digital marketing, where time is money and efficiency is king, FusionAds.ai emerges as a revolutionary AI-powered platform designed to streamline the advertising process for businesses and agencies alike. Its core functionality lies in generating and publishing professional ads in mere seconds. Aimed at both seasoned marketers and those with no prior marketing experience, FusionAds.ai simplifies the creation of omnichannel content with just a single click, ensuring that your campaigns are not only high-quality but also highly effective.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2026-04-09T20-15-56.078Z-rZQsxQjPt6aiODa1NaBPiCYk4fhzoKaXm.png', 'https://l.fusionos.ai/iIEtRevd9Nb', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Subscription Plans", "price": "$10 per month", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Generative AI Advertising","One-Click Content Creation","A/B Testing Automation","No Experience Required"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
