('Quizgecko', 'quizgecko', 'Transforms content into quizzes, flashcards, and podcasts.', 'Quizgecko is an innovative AI-driven platform designed to revolutionize the way quizzes, flashcards, and study materials are created and utilized. By leveraging advanced AI technology, Quizgecko transforms various content formats into interactive quizzes, flashcards, podcasts, and study notes. This tool is tailored for students, educators, and businesses looking to optimize learning and assessment processes, making it easier to generate, customize, and distribute educational content efficiently.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2026-02-27T11-14-41.760Z-MjM0OO-KMgVCTmatriaU6mT95SQ5Rk6Dn.png', 'https://quizgecko.com/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Basic", "price": "$0 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Premium", "price": "$16 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Ultra", "price": "$29 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Organization", "price": "Custom", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI Question Generator","AI Flashcard Generator","AI Podcast Generator","Customizable Study Tools","Comprehensive Content Transformation","User-Friendly Interface"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
