('AI Text Humanizer', 'ai-text-humanizer', 'Transforms AI-generated text into natural, human-like language.', 'AI Text Humanizer revolutionizes the way we interact with AI-generated content by transforming it into natural, human-like text. This tool is specifically designed to help users bypass AI detectors by turning machine-generated prose from platforms like ChatGPT, Claude, or Jasper into convincing, readable text. It''s an ideal solution for students, writers, marketers, and anyone needing to polish AI-generated content for better readability and acceptance.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2025-01-24T17-35-45.062Z-9FIUYXoZ89ze-QRRbFGaGC6IPG8z3bLJH.png', 'https://ai-text-humanizer.com/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Humanization of AI Content","AI Detector Bypass","Readability Enhancement","API Access for PRO Users","Time Efficiency","User-Friendly Interface"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
('AI Prompt Library', 'ai-prompt-library', 'Enhance AI interactions with 30,000+ tailored prompts.', 'AI Prompt Library, offered by God of Prompt, is a comprehensive collection of expertly crafted AI prompts designed to enhance the utility of platforms like ChatGPT and Midjourney. This tool is specifically tailored for businesses and professionals looking to streamline operations, boost productivity, and maximize the potential of AI technologies. By providing over 30,000 prompts across various categories such as marketing, SEO, and productivity, AI Prompt Library simplifies the task of generating high-quality content and strategies, making it an invaluable resource for users aiming to optimize their AI interactions.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2026-02-27T11-14-03.365Z-XVDb-ujjfzC8aaXCyDkKMtISHXn7mNVAT.png', 'https://godofprompt.ai/pricing', 'freemium', '[]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Extensive Prompt Collection","Category-Specific Bundles","Regular Updates","Comprehensive Guides and Resources","Time Efficiency","Cost-Effective Solutions"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
('Mumble Note', 'mumble-note', 'Transforms spoken words into structured notes instantly.', 'Mumble Note is your go-to AI voice notetaker designed to transform spoken words into structured notes, tasks, and outputs instantly. Whether you''re capturing meeting details, brainstorming ideas, or jotting down quick notes, Mumble Note simplifies the process, making it ideal for professionals and creatives who thrive on efficiency and innovation.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2026-02-04T13-20-49.961Z-y6olx2-R02rS5JUZzAeGzZ064_Vs7L_Y2.webp', 'https://www.mumblenote.com/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Monthly", "price": "$15.00 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Annual", "price": "$119.99 per year", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI-Driven Transcriptions","Task Automation","Multi-Format Note Capture","Language Support"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
