('Angry Email Translator', 'angry-email-translator', 'Transforms angry emails to professional; enhances communication with AI-powered rephrasing.', 'In the digital age where email communication is paramount, the Angry Email Translator emerges as a beacon of diplomacy and understanding. This unique AI tool is ingeniously designed to transform heated or negatively-toned emails into professional, polite, and constructive messages. It''s a godsend for individuals and professionals alike who seek to maintain harmony and effectiveness in their digital correspondence.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/d28eb6c53d15ca43c3a9f80c8c2ca46e38b41f30-2533x1269.jpg', 'https://angryemailtranslator.com/', 'free', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Emotion Detection","Content Rewriting","Tone Adjustment","Multilingual Support","Improved Communication","Time-Saving"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
