('Eightfold', 'eightfold', 'AI-driven platform optimizing recruitment, retention, and workforce planning.', 'Eightfold is reshaping the talent management landscape by leveraging AI to streamline recruitment, retention, and overall workforce planning. Designed for HR professionals and organizations of all sizes, Eightfold simplifies the intricacies of talent acquisition and management, offering a comprehensive platform that integrates AI-driven insights to optimize hiring and employee development.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/179810bb2d7486fea9270b797005a2b1b8cfc84e-2532x1222.png', 'https://eightfold.ai/', 'contact', '[{"plan": "Custom Pricing", "price": "Custom", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI-Powered Talent Matching","Diversity and Bias Mitigation","Comprehensive Talent Database","Career Site Personalization","Enhanced Recruitment Efficiency","Improved Candidate Experience"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
